{
  "stem": "20609.3",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 12.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "So now it's life goes on.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "It's April 13th or 14th, I believe it was, 1945.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "The evening, we got a report-- we get-- we get an order from the Jewish elders.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "By the way, the original elder Epstein was shot in 1945 because he-- he protested the transports.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "So they made his second in command [INAUDIBLE]-- he just disappeared.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "He was shot in the basement of the commandant's office.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And-- and then [INAUDIBLE] became the elder.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "He was a real piece of garbage.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "He was really one of the most hated people in the world.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And Rabbi Beck was still there, he was still in the elders, and he was exempt from transport.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "We had a Danish rabbi, the chief rabbi.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "There was only one rabbi in Denmark.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "He went-- was also exempt, you know.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And-- well, we didn't know why we were exempt.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "We just-- we just thought we were lucky not to go.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And so [DRINKS] --we got notified on the night of April 13th, we have to be at six o'clock in the morning at the place what they used to call the appel, where you assemble for transport, all right.",
      "word_count": 39
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "Nothing else-- there was no reason giving and everything.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "Now, one guy hid.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "One guy didn't report.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "And-- and you really can't hide in a place like that because-- unless you-- you have enough provision and things which nobody ever had, you know.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So this guy says, I don't trust these guys, you know.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So he hid.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And he didn't go and report.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So next morning we stood there and they had-- had a row of tables set up and this time it was not Czechoslovakian guys.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "All SS were sitting there, checked our numbers against the list they had.",
      "word_count": 13
    }
  ],
